name: Tailwind CSS Tokens
description:
Meet the free set featuring the latest and the most comprehensive list of default styles coming with Tailwind CSS 2.0. Each of the styles titled following

the Tailwind CSS naming convention for smoother design-to-development hand-off.


Streamline your prototyping with 222 colour styles, 108 text styles and 448 icons. Turn it into a library to include into any project.
